[[/=]]

**Date:** 9/03/2033

[Begin Log]
------

**O5-6:** I'm sorry if I sound paranoid or narcissistic, but why exactly am I the only one here that is at least a tad bit skeptical about this whole thing.

**O5-3:** You do sound paranoid.

**O5-1:** Well... would you like to tell us why you are so skeptical.

**O5-4:** There usually isn't a reason with people like this. They always find a reason to go against real progress.

**O5-10:** True.

**O5-6:** Don't you all see that. This is exactly what I'm talking about. Don't any of you think this is just a tad involuntarily hive-mindish?

**O5-5:** Well that does sound paranoid...

**O5-6:** You voted against the reintegration of this research alongside me. You were pushing it back harder than me.

**O5-5:** The difference between me and then is that now I see its potential.

**O5-6:** This is a fucking gamble! Why are we doing this?

**O5-1:** My friend, this is no gamble. The prosthetic arm has been consistent in every trial. There is nothing to fear.

**O5-6:** It's an anomaly... that's enough reason to fear it.

**O5-7:** It's just one attempt and if it does go wrong... well, it was worth the gamble. Besides we've dealt with so many world-ending anomalies with a small number of casualties. I'm sure we could deal with another.

**O5-6:** You and everyone else are missing the point. Why do we have to take this risk?

**O5-8:** We've always taken risks. How is this any different from the others?

**O5-6:** Necessity is the difference.

**O5-1:** But this is necessary, my friend. It may not make sense to you now but I'm sure it will soon.

**O5-6:** This... is... stupid.

**O5-13:** Can we hurry and vote? The outcome has already been decided. Let's just move the pleasantries out of the way.

**O5-1:** Agreed, if you all are ready I shall begin. Yea.

**O5-2:** Yea.

**O5-3:** Yea.

**O5-4:** Yea.

**O5-5:** Yea.

**O5-6:** Nay...

**O5-7:** Yea.

**O5-8:** Yea.

**O5-9:** Yea.

**O5-10:** Yea.

**O5-11:** Yea.

**O5-12:**Abstain.

**O5-13:** Yea.

**O5-1:** Thank you. Proj. Gambler's Fallacy has now been approved to move forward to the final stage. O5-13 will be supervising the experiment. Until we all meet again.

------
[End Log]
